snippet.title: Elementallis Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Elementallis on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/1304280/Elementallis/

Elementallis is a classic top down adventure with a modernized retro aesthetic. Explore a vast world and conquer the dungeons to obtain all the Elements and use them to solve puzzles and defeat your foes.

Trailer music by Raúl Sangonzalo - https://soundcloud.com/raul-sangonzalo


Links of interest:
Discord: https://discord.gg/elementallis
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1304280/Elementallis/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/elementallis
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Elementallis
Website: http://elementallis.com
